column5: Hey guys,  ive never rented a boat before, dont think it could be that hard.  Does anyone know a marina or place where i can get a small boat to rent for saturday on LAKE CHEMONG, in the Kawarthas?  Any help is appreciated THANKS.  Pachone
Star Marine on the east end of the causeway always had a sign that advertised boat rentals, at least up until last year, but I can't offer anymore than that.
